<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Students may receive exemptions and/or credit for a score of 5 on Advanced Placement Examinations. Scores will be reviewed in conjunction with all other application materials, including academic transcripts and portfolio. Placement and exemption from humanities and studio course requirements will not be automatic. Credit awards and exemptions will be assessed on an individual, case-by-case basis. Portfolio score of 3 or higher required for studio credit.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.sva.edu/attend-sva/undergraduate/faq" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
